data.description: Welcome to 81 Oakdale Street, a stunning lakefront home located along the famous Butler Chain of Lakes on the Lake Down Canal. This magnificent custom built estate offers the perfect blend of elegance, modern amenities, and exceptional craftsmanship. Situated on a peaceful and spacious corner lot with an adjoining pond. This home is located on one of the very few paved roads in Downtown Windermere, providing both privacy and convenience. As you walk through the front door, you'll be greeted by a grand foyer with soaring ceilings, Brazilian cherry & travertine floors, and an abundance of natural light. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. The stylishly designed kitchen boasts high-end appliances, custom cabinetry, granite countertops, and a center island, making it a chef's dream. Owners willing to provide rate buy down if under contract by 12/1/2023! This home features 5 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms and a bonus loft space. The primary suite offers a serene sanctuary with an oversized room, a bonus space perfect for a nursery, home gym or study; a spa-like en-suite bathroom complete with a soaking tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities and a large walk-in closet. Each bedroom is generously sized, with ample closet space and large windows that showcase the picturesque views of the surrounding landscape. Indulge in lakefront living at it’s finest in the expansive backyard oasis. The newly extended patio is perfect for al fresco dining, entertaining or relaxing by the expansive 60” wood burning fire pit. Enjoy the day taking your boat or jet skis out for a spin with the private boat dock equipped with an electric motor to enjoy “Florida’s Most Outstanding Waters”. In addition to the beautiful indoor and outdoor living spaces you will be delighted to know that this home includes pre-wiring for audio in the first floor entertaining spaces including the screened in outdoor patio. You’ll enjoy an extra deep garage with a golf cart bay, parking for an RV or trailer, energy efficient and insulated concrete form walls. A roof that is only 4 years old, 2 new AC units, all new garage doors and motors, fresh paint indoors & out and a recently serviced septic system and all with no HOA. Windermere is known for it’s small town charm, top rated schools, The Butler Chain of Lakes, and a bustling downtown with events like the weekly Farmers Market, Family Food Truck Night, and the Windermere Wine & Dine. You will enjoy cobblestone streets lined with boutiques, coffee shops, restaurants, and recreational facilities made up of tennis courts, playgrounds, boat ramps and walking trails. Don't miss the opportunity to make 81 Oakdale Street yours and experience the epitome of luxury living among the lakes. Make sure to check out the property video & matterport.
